name: Jump too High
description:
Jump too High v. 2.0.0

'Jump too High' is a mini-game.

The aim is to convey the character to the top of the game.

During the play you'll meet opponents.

Keep you away from them and you will win.

Good luck. :)

Update v. 2.0.0 (Dec. 2015):

-> New backgroundmusic

-> New number of meters

-> Fixed many bugs

-> Much better control
